    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port=host:port<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target IP
