    Note over Sidecar: Generate x-request-id (UUID)
    Note over Sidecar: Modify request: stream=false,<br/>max_tokens=1, add kv_transfer_params

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(modified request with kv_transfer_params)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Optional TLS 1.2+
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>(block IDs, engine ID, host, port)

    Note over Sidecar: Augment original request with<br/>prefiller's kv_transfer_params

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(original + kv_transfer_params)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming token response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streaming response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefiller Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward request directly<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 3: Passthrough (Non-Completion Endpoints)

    Client->>Sidecar: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Passthrough reverse proxy<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 4: SSRF Protection Rejection

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port=evil:port
    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target IP
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Denied (IP not in allowlist)
    Sidecar-->>Client: HTTP 403 Forbidden
